data.description: Welcome to this darling home in Ocean Shores. This home offers 3 large bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, hardwood floors, large laundry room, wood burning stove and an open concept. Outside you will find a large front and back deck for entertaining, fully fenced back yard, 2 storage sheds, peek-a-boo views of the bay and its all situated on a very large corner lot to make your landscaping dreams come true.
